<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    {% set css %}
    {% include "style.css" %}
    {% endset %}
    <style>
      {{css | cssmin | safe}}</style>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weird Website Lovers Webring</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Weird Website Lovers Webring</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>A webring for everyone who loves weird websites. There's something special about those sites that have one joke, or very unusual CSS, or are just plain weird.
        <a href="https://forms.gle/oRBKcfZ6wjqEzZ819" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Join now!</a>
      </p>
      <h2>Members</h2>
      <ol class="flow">
        {% for site in sites %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ site.URL }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ site["Website title"] }}</a>
            <p>{{ site["Website description"] }}</p>
            <p>Owner: {{ site["Owner name"] }}
            </p>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>
      <h2>Code snippet</h2>
      <p>Members, put this snippet on your website to display the webring! You can style it however you want. It'll look
        something like this:</p>
      <div class="webring-container">
        <span aria-hidden>ü™ê</span>
        <p>Part of the
          <a href="https://weirdwebsitelovers.neocities.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Weird Website Lovers
            Webring</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://webring.sophiekoonin.workers.dev/prev">Previous</a>
          <a href="https://webring.sophiekoonin.workers.dev/next">Next</a>
          <a href="https://webring.sophiekoonin.workers.dev/random" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Random</a>
          <a href="https://weirdwebsitelovers.neocities.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Members</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <textarea readonly rows="6">
        <div class="webring-container">
          <span aria-hidden>ü™ê</span>
          <p>Part of the
            <a href="https://weirdwebsitelovers.neocities.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Weird Website Lovers
              Webring</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://webring.sophiekoonin.workers.dev/prev">Previous</a>
            <a href="https://webring.sophiekoonin.workers.dev/next">Next</a>
            <a href="https://webring.sophiekoonin.workers.dev/random" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Random</a>
            <a href="https://weirdwebsitelovers.neocities.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Members</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </textarea>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>Created by
        <a href="https://localghost.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sophie</a>
        for a talk demo</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>